data.description: Welcome to your COMPLETELY UPDATED Home Sweet Home with low maintenance & easy living! Attention to detail does not go unnoticed. Immediately greeted by a large and inviting front porch with fresh updates & freshly manicured landscaping. Inside you will find  a spacious living area & dining room with a beautifully constructed sliding barnwood style door. Spacious kitchen has been completely updated with high-end finishings (new flooring, refinished cabinetry, countertops, undermount sink) & brand new stainless steel appliances. Large windows allow for plenty of natural light. Full bathroom on the first floor that has also been completely updated (new flooring, shower install, flooring & vanity). Frist floor primary bedroom with new flooring. An oversized bedroom upstairs that could double as an at-home office or extra space. Don't forgot the upgraded mudroom off the backdoor. Unwind in the picture perfect backyard (partial fenced, large storage shed, & large grape arbor)
